---
title: Lemongrass Beef Strips with soy glazed veg and jasmine rice
description: Fragrant rice forms the base of this Asian-inspired beef dish. Lemongrass—another aromatic ingredient—is the shining flavour, while vibrant veg adds a satisfying crunch as well as all-important nutrients.
